If you can't use the full featured Forscan program for Windows 10 with extended license or do and just need something more mobile then Forscan Lite is a must have for all Ford & Lincoln owners. Don't waste your time with any other apps on the mobile market not even the official free manufacturer apps if you want access to all the tools the dealership charges you big money to run for you on their computer. The Forscan team have given priceless software tools to the community of owners, these programs are not the same as the gimmicky read only access apps on the market, these are technician grade tools specially written for all Ford\Lincoln(Mazda too I think) vehicles with access to PATS and other modules no other software in the free\cheap consumer grade market can access at all never mind perform all service functions and tests the dealership has access to like the Forscan team have done. As a Lincoln LS owner using Forscan I have saved easily $500 in dealership bills and time without my car. Forscan has even outperformed Ford's own IDS software in programming my keyless entry fob that can only be programmed at the dealership (no ignition cycle for Gen 1 LS owners).
This is an amazing tool. I was able to dive into many of the settings on my vehicles at I wanted to change. The information available is almost overwhelming.

This app is great in that it has many of the Ford specific PIDs built in. A first improvement that would be nice is to be able to configure a custom PID (e.g. missing boost PID:ff1202). Secondly, it would be nice to modify the logged PIDs list without having the OBD hooked up to the vehicle. Nice app; great for datalogging Ford-specific info from multiple computer modules. I would like to see it go a little further in functionality like min/max value logging, but very pleased so far!
